{"tid":1649540,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"沈旭暉:「香港に栄光あれ」","createTime":"2019-10-12T16:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T07:17:04.000Z","uid":304288,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bd72afb8121e53fc924664e2382d6988270506","tid":1649540,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"有跟開生活台嘅大家應該知尋晚沈旭暉以guest身份喺日本東大開talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身為喺日本讀緊書嘅漢奸死曱甴，我當然去咗見大師一面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2LhWSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2LhWSZ.png&h=cb2b7fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在場大半係日本人學生 (一部份好似係佢哋教授compulsory要佢哋出席)、有幾個比較開通嘅大陸人、十幾個應該係教授嘅人(日本人同外國人都有)、同大概十個香港人學生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">演講內容</span></span><br />\n日本人教授主要講解咗反送中運動嘅起因同發展，除咗無提及到LIHKG嘅存在之外，其他野講得幾詳盡，其間仲聽到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟著細佬想報告吓沈旭暉個talk嘅內容<br />\n佢前半主要講咗香港嘅背景，香港嘅國際地位、重要性、獨特之處，香港人點睇自己嘅身份等等。以下為細佬有限能力之下記得嘅少少重點（部份字眼經小弟我翻譯返做人話，絕非大師嘅exact wording嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)：<br />\n- 背景有英殖時期，回歸，一國兩制等嘅內容<br />\n- 回歸之後，香港可以分為幾個時期<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港時期</span>(全部時期嘅命名係我起嘅，唔係大師起嘅)<br />\n   &rarr;曾蔭權、董建華為英殖時期時訓練出嚟嘅精英，在職期間為一個非常「香港」嘅時期<br />\n   &rarr;其間，由回歸之後中共第一次開始搞香港，係喺香港人舉行咗第一次遊行，中共feel倒唔妥之後<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: red;\">中國香港時期</span><br />\n   &rarr;下一個時期就係689上任之後。執政方式同行政方針開始轉向中國化，令好多香港人不滿<br />\n   &rarr;跟住就到依家隻林閪月娥。上任初期睇落比較平穩，直至2019 6月為止<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: blue;\">獨裁者2.0時期</span><br />\n   &rarr;2019 6月到依家為止，點解咁叫就唔使細佬解釋吧。<br />\n<br />\n尾聲為今次運動可以以咩形式完，同香港未來會係點。以下為point form要點：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Conflict Resolution?</span><br />\n- Conventional Government Approach (which is the most common solution in the world)<br />\n    &bull;independent commission of investigation<br />\n    &bull;reform of police force (need not be complete reform)<br />\n    &bull;reorganisation of government<br />\n    &bull;unconditional amnesty of both sides<br />\n- Traditional Democratic Approach (unlikely to happen)<br />\n- Communist Approach (同上)<br />\n- Revolutionary Approach (no matter which side wins, there will be complete collapse of current government and system) <br />\n- Long-term Stalemate (change gradually)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Future of Hong Kong, Futuristic</span><br />\n- Development of a sustainable economic ecosystem (don&rsquo;t have to merely depend on Chinese company anymore)<br />\n- Evolving geographical concept: time-space compression and the engagement of diasporic community <br />\n- Evolving identity construction process in the virtual community <br />\n- The concept of &ldquo;Chartered cities&rdquo; of Paul Romer<br />\n- 6G world order and Kingsman<br />\n<br />\n最後佢用日文多謝關心香港嘅每一位聽眾，再喺最最最後講咗句「香港に栄光あれ」(願榮光歸香港) 收尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我對眼係撚咁流汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A之後</span><br />\nQ&amp;A之後，有兩個香港人學生出咗去做少少補充同解釋，另外講咗一啲兩位教授唔方便講嘅野(離奇被自殺、示威者嘅諗法等)。入面有2點想同大家分享吓：<br />\n1）大陸嘅教育入面，有3樣任何人都不得接受嘅大惡，分別係&rdquo;separatism&rdquo;(分裂主義), &ldquo;terrorism&rdquo;(恐怖主義)同&ldquo;extremism&rdquo;(極端主義)。而依家香港嘅示威，喺內睦正正係俾中共文宣(屈)到食正尼三惡。尼個應該係大部份大陸人對我哋咁反感嘅主要原因<br />\n2）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">關於混大陸公安同解放軍入去香港警隊入面，其實係完全合法的。</span><br />\n對於第二點，講緊嘅就即係係咁屌同質問佢哋放人入警隊係無用嘅。細佬覺得大家應該集中返喺中共點解要「偷偷地」混人入嚟，而唔光明正大做。個原因其實好簡單。中國依家喺國際上係行緊「和平主義」路線，所以即使混人入警隊係合法，佢都唔可以俾世界知/覺得佢喺度<span style=\"color: red;\">直接</span>用武力介入緊香港嘅事務。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小弟覺得與其繼續屌上面混人入嚟香港警隊，不如搵啲有力嘅證據，嚟幫中共文宣下佢嘅所謂「和平主義」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">六大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1c689beb6810064c47681cc221c0b86fdc4e566","tid":1649540,"uid":176567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1abbaa15d1de237705ecd8be94f479e52ff8330e","tid":1649540,"uid":304288,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0bd72afb8121e53fc924664e2382d6988270506","tid":1649540,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"有跟開生活台嘅大家應該知尋晚沈旭暉以guest身份喺日本東大開talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身為喺日本讀緊書嘅漢奸死曱甴，我當然去咗見大師一面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2LhWSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2LhWSZ.png&h=cb2b7fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在場大半係日本人學生 (一部份好似係佢哋教授compulsory要佢哋出席)、有幾個比較開通嘅大陸人、十幾個應該係教授嘅人(日本人同外國人都有)、同大概十個香港人學生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">演講內容</span></span><br />\n日本人教授主要講解咗反送中運動嘅起因同發展，除咗無提及到LIHKG嘅存在之外，其他野講得幾詳盡，其間仲聽到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟著細佬想報告吓沈旭暉個talk嘅內容<br />\n佢前半主要講咗香港嘅背景，香港嘅國際地位、重要性、獨特之處，香港人點睇自己嘅身份等等。以下為細佬有限能力之下記得嘅少少重點（部份字眼經小弟我翻譯返做人話，絕非大師嘅exact wording嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)：<br />\n- 背景有英殖時期，回歸，一國兩制等嘅內容<br />\n- 回歸之後，香港可以分為幾個時期<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港時期</span>(全部時期嘅命名係我起嘅，唔係大師起嘅)<br />\n   &rarr;曾蔭權、董建華為英殖時期時訓練出嚟嘅精英，在職期間為一個非常「香港」嘅時期<br />\n   &rarr;其間，由回歸之後中共第一次開始搞香港，係喺香港人舉行咗第一次遊行，中共feel倒唔妥之後<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: red;\">中國香港時期</span><br />\n   &rarr;下一個時期就係689上任之後。執政方式同行政方針開始轉向中國化，令好多香港人不滿<br />\n   &rarr;跟住就到依家隻林閪月娥。上任初期睇落比較平穩，直至2019 6月為止<br />\n   &rarr;<span style=\"color: blue;\">獨裁者2.0時期</span><br />\n   &rarr;2019 6月到依家為止，點解咁叫就唔使細佬解釋吧。<br />\n<br />\n尾聲為今次運動可以以咩形式完，同香港未來會係點。以下為point form要點：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Conflict Resolution?</span><br />\n- Conventional Government Approach (which is the most common solution in the world)<br />\n    &bull;independent commission of investigation<br />\n    &bull;reform of police force (need not be complete reform)<br />\n    &bull;reorganisation of government<br />\n    &bull;unconditional amnesty of both sides<br />\n- Traditional Democratic Approach (unlikely to happen)<br />\n- Communist Approach (同上)<br />\n- Revolutionary Approach (no matter which side wins, there will be complete collapse of current government and system) <br />\n- Long-term Stalemate (change gradually)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Future of Hong Kong, Futuristic</span><br />\n- Development of a sustainable economic ecosystem (don&rsquo;t have to merely depend on Chinese company anymore)<br />\n- Evolving geographical concept: time-space compression and the engagement of diasporic community <br />\n- Evolving identity construction process in the virtual community <br />\n- The concept of &ldquo;Chartered cities&rdquo; of Paul Romer<br />\n- 6G world order and Kingsman<br />\n<br />\n最後佢用日文多謝關心香港嘅每一位聽眾，再喺最最最後講咗句「香港に栄光あれ」(願榮光歸香港) 收尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我對眼係撚咁流汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A之後</span><br />\nQ&amp;A之後，有兩個香港人學生出咗去做少少補充同解釋，另外講咗一啲兩位教授唔方便講嘅野(離奇被自殺、示威者嘅諗法等)。入面有2點想同大家分享吓：<br />\n1）大陸嘅教育入面，有3樣任何人都不得接受嘅大惡，分別係&rdquo;separatism&rdquo;(分裂主義), &ldquo;terrorism&rdquo;(恐怖主義)同&ldquo;extremism&rdquo;(極端主義)。而依家香港嘅示威，喺內睦正正係俾中共文宣(屈)到食正尼三惡。尼個應該係大部份大陸人對我哋咁反感嘅主要原因<br />\n2）<span style=\"font-size: large;\">關於混大陸公安同解放軍入去香港警隊入面，其實係完全合法的。</span><br />\n對於第二點，講緊嘅就即係係咁屌同質問佢哋放人入警隊係無用嘅。細佬覺得大家應該集中返喺中共點解要「偷偷地」混人入嚟，而唔光明正大做。個原因其實好簡單。中國依家喺國際上係行緊「和平主義」路線，所以即使混人入警隊係合法，佢都唔可以俾世界知/覺得佢喺度<span style=\"color: red;\">直接</span>用武力介入緊香港嘅事務。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小弟覺得與其繼續屌上面混人入嚟香港警隊，不如搵啲有力嘅證據，嚟幫中共文宣下佢嘅所謂「和平主義」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">六大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"中段嘅內容我錄音斷咗，如果有其他在場嘅巴絲入咗嚟嘅話幫幫手總結下<br />\n<br />\n上面爆咗字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺度補返個Q&amp;A先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A session</span><br />\n其中一個大陸學生問：「兄弟爬山入面，佢哋尼班大陸年輕人係『兄弟』定係『山』？」<br />\n細佬覺得只要有腦嘅，無論你係邊度嚟，都可以係兄弟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果無腦嘅，就算你係香港嚟，你都係座山嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 細佬P牌仔第一次開po，有咩做錯各位巴絲記得大大力屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (sorry for 1999 also)"},{"pid":"626417339bd9123b5f1835db4d66113ceccdf6f3","tid":1649540,"uid":240607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:57:57.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d75b1c8f03938aacd053d9fb82dace4ce04ab58a","tid":1649540,"uid":274302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:59:16.000Z","msg":"巴打寫得好啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e088a161e81f631a9a43e2362b6e1b3f7c84a8d","tid":1649540,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"推，多謝傳送消息"},{"pid":"0086081ef1b537bda2c48ed0feca171a93e9fba7","tid":1649540,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非聽日出動前可唔可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n去警總關心下銀髮族</span>？帶啲食物丶水（寶礦力）同退熱貼之類去？</span>"},{"pid":"e9dc1bf1ae0f5f2a966ab0093d984600bc8f1e15","tid":1649540,"uid":214312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b670583b54d86f1a66b64e83089f6a78753aac78","tid":1649540,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db54535a5f694a13e40e68d7b4c8ce6eceaedbac","tid":1649540,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75b1c8f03938aacd053d9fb82dace4ce04ab58a","tid":1649540,"uid":274302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:59:16.000Z","msg":"巴打寫得好啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望碌鳩脫完皮會生返塊新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo